                &lt;p&gt;Safari Technology Preview Release 27 is now available for download for macOS Sierra.&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;tag safari&quot;&gt;safari&lt;/span&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class=&quot;table__content&quot;&gt;
